summary:
◈

Apollo armor set
◈

: 5% increase in physical and arcane defense  slight boost to physical attacks 15% increase in dexterity...
caption:
◈ Apollo armor set ◈ :

  • 5% increase in physical and arcane defense
  • slight boost to physical attacks
  • 15% increase in dexterity
  • 100% decrease in stealth

[made of gilded adamantine steel, lumen cloth and citrine quartz]

Apollo is one of Dan’s favorite armor sets, but due to its brilliant hues, contrasting sharply with the usual dark color schemes he favors, as well as the lack of any true defensive power in battle, it’s one he rarely equips.

The design was inspired by Dan’s tweet a while back in reference to the Met gala when he imagined himself rolling up to the event and “throwing off a gilded cape to reveal surgically attached angel wings and a tux made of bedazzled dove feathers.”
